data.description: Great Opportunity for Affordable Living in The Heart of Pensacola. Home Offers: Open Living; High Ceilings; Eat-in Kitchen/Dining; Fireplace in the Living Room; Master Bedroom on the Main Floor and Bedroom Loft is Upstairs. The Shared Staircase Leads to the Oversized One Car Garage. This Condominium Complex is Managed by Liberty Community Management which Takes Care of Grounds Keeping; Exterior Maintenance; Community Pool; and Garbage. Some Improvements are Already Underway.  Home is Near Shopping, Dining, the Airport, and Interstate 10.  SELLER WILL PAINT INTERIOR WALLS WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER (BUYER'S CHOICE OF COLOR).
